            "list": [
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/26/25750596/6abf9e6af33d5811e9e008d451a6a180_6327412572973273172.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>In Subzero Climate, you will continuously accumulate Sheer Cold. When Sheer Cold reaches its limit, your character will <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">start rapidly losing HP</span>. Apart from that, due to Dragonspine's unique Ley Line structure and climate, you may be <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">unable to use</span> some gadgets.</p>",
                "key": "Page 1/3"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/26/25750596/d518442ea2c77ca1cfe2a27840f07661_4236247660379564299.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Bonfires and other sources of heat will <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">diminish Sheer Cold</span>. <br>There might be also special items that lessen the effects of Sheer Cold.</p>",
                "key": "Page 2/3"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/26/25750596/2e17a0d78887602dd496487112e7bfdf_9021496199459590425.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Certain conditions like Snowstorms and actions like swimming will accelerate Sheer Cold's accumulation.<br>Carefully plan your route ahead of time to make sure you'll survive a trip through Subzero Climate.</p>",
                "key": "Page 3/3"
              }
            ],
